    <div class="ic-container">
      <div class="evo-section-head">
        <span class="evo-badge">FAQ</span>
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="evo-faq__grid">
        
        <div class="evo-faq-item">
          <h4>How does remote IT support work?</h4>
          <p>We use industry-standard remote access tools (with your permission) to connect to your computer and resolve issues directly — just as if a technician were sitting beside you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="evo-faq-item">
          <h4>Is remote support secure?</h4>
          <p>Yes. All remote sessions are encrypted, session-recorded, and require your explicit permission to initiate. We never connect to your device without your approval.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="evo-faq-item">
          <h4>Can you support staff working from home across different Perth suburbs?</h4>
          <p>Absolutely. Remote support is location-independent — we support your team whether they're in the CBD, Joondalup, Fremantle, or working interstate.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} CTA {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="evo-cta">
    <div class="ic-container">
      <div class="evo-cta__inner">
