          <p>Book a <strong style="color:#cff394">free, no-obligation consultation</strong> with EvoTech Digital. Perth-based experts ready to help your business.</p>
          <div class="evo-cta__checks">
            <div class="evo-cta__check">Free consultation — no obligation, no pressure</div>
            <div class="evo-cta__check">Custom quote within 24 hours</div>
            <div class="evo-cta__check">Perth-based team, not an overseas call centre</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="evo-cta__btns">
          <a href="{{ section.settings.cta_primary_link }}" class="evo-btn-cta evo-btn-cta--lime">📧 View Support Plans</a>
